{"word":"ἔσω","slug":"ἔσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔσω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘located within a space’ <b>within, inside <a href='B:470 26:58'>Mt 26:58</a>; <a href='B:480 14:54'>Mk 14:54</a>; <a href='B:480 15:16'>15:16</a>; <a href='B:500 20:26'>J 20:26</a>; <a href='B:510 5:23'>Ac 5:23</a>.</b> By extension, of a spiritual condition <b>inner <a href='B:520 7:22'>Ro 7:22</a>; <a href='B:540 4:16'>2 Cor 4:16</a>; <a href='B:560 3:16'>Eph 3:16</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘closely connected’, <el>ἔ.</el> as opposed to <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔξω\">ἔξω</a></el>, <b>inside:</b> <el>οἱ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔσω\">ἔσω</a></el> insiders, namely members of the congregation <b><a href='B:530 5:12'>1 Cor 5:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔσχηκα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔσωθεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}